i## Fixing Paths in Open5GS Configuration Files under NixOS		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
iSince Open5GS packaged in Nixpkgs is installed by default under a path		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
iin `/nix/store` , its configuration files also references many paths		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
iunder `/nix/store` by default.		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
iFirst, get the actual installation path of Open5GS:		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
