i# Modifying Open5GS Configuration Files		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
iAfter Open5GS is installed, you will need to modify the configuration		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
ifiles to match the parameters of our CBRS LTE network. We only need to		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
imake the following changes:		{{server_addr}}	{{server_port}}
